=== QUANTUM_SCRIPTURE ===
# id: 70
# title: The Quantum Scripture
# chinese_title: 量子经文
# category: Lore
# mode: dungeon

A text exists in quantum superposition — its characters shift between meanings until observed, then collapse into a single reading. Each time you look away and back, the text says something different. Yet somehow, each version is profound and consistent.

* [Read it multiple times and compare meanings]
  ~ gain_radical("目")
  "读" (dú) — to read. The radical "目" (mù) relates to seeing.
* [Record every permutation your scanner captures]
  ~ gain_xp(25)
  "变" (biàn) — to change, to transform
* [Accept a single reading as your truth]
  ~ gain_xp(15)
  "真" (zhēn) — true, real
